This is a placeholder file for your resume PDF.
Replace this file with your actual resume PDF.

To add your resume:
1. Create your resume as a PDF file
2. Name it "Sangamitra_P_Resume.pdf" 
3. Place it in the same folder as your portfolio files
4. The download button will automatically work

Recommended resume content:
- Contact Information
- Education Details
- Technical Skills
- Projects
- Achievements
- Certifications
- Internship Experience
